parameters: Banka "Whoa! Kru-san! What are you doing in a place like this!"
Kru "Whoa! My bad, my bad! I'm really sorry!"
Banka "That's not cool! You ruined a good moment!"
Kru "Well... Umi has gone somewhere... and I was looking for her..."
Banka "Huh? You think she's cheating on you with me, is that why you came?"
Banka "Yes! ...By the way, didn't you say you saw Umi-san earlier?"
Villager "Yes... near the altar of Chancellor Shif..."
Banka "Then maybe she's praying? Please go and fetch her."
Kru "I see... thanks, you've been a big help."
